title: Crosby Stills Nash - 2015-10-01 - Milan
description:
Here is another nice bootleg. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)


Crosby, Stills & Nash
Milan, Italy
Teatro degli Arcimboldi
Oktober 01, 2015


DPA SMK4061 -> DPA MPS6020 -> Edirol R-09HR (24 bit/96 kHz) >
Adobe Audition CS6 (normalize by peak levels; clapping attenuated;
talk raised; Fade in and fade out applied) ->
CD Wave (track splitting) -> Steinberg Wavelab LE7 (16-bit Conversion)->
TLH (Flac16 Conversion @ level 8)
Taper: Trainsrus
